To install the django first your system must have latest python  version.

after installing python open command prompt and enter the following command.

>>>python -m pip install -U pip

Your system must have a environment to store your django projects.

To install that enter the following command.

>>>pip install virtualenv

after that set virtual environment by doing the following commands

>>>virtualenv nameofvirtualenvironment

change directory 

>>>cd nameofvirtualenvironment

change directory to the Scripts and activate virtual environment

>>>cd Scripts

>>>activate

